OL,3,CMan 'pointed out homes of migrant
OL,4,Cneighbours' for attacks, court told
OL,6,FA Belfast man allegedly pointed out
OL,7,Fthe homes of migrant neighbours living
OL,8,Fon his street to be attacked with
OL,9,Fhammers, the High Court heard on
OL,10,FTuesday.
OL,12,FCraig Watson is accused of being part
OL,13,Fof a masked crowd who targeted houses
OL,14,Fin the north of the city earlier this
OL,15,Fmonth.
OL,17,FBut the 41-year-old claims he only
OL,18,Fidentified his own home at Rathlin
OL,19,FStreet in a bid to ensure local
OL,20,Floyalist paramilitaries left it alone.
