OL,3,CMan 'pointed out homes of migrant
OL,4,Cneighbours' for attacks, court told
OL,6,FWatson is charged with two counts of
OL,7,Fcriminal damage and incitement to
OL,8,Fhatred over the racially-motivated
OL,9,Fincident on August 6.
OL,11,FHe was refused bail due to the risk of
OL,12,Fre-offending.
OL,14,FThe court heard up to eight men
OL,15,Fwearing balaclavas attacked two houses
OL,16,Fon Rathlin Street with hammers,
OL,17,Fcausing extensive damage to front
OL,18,Fdoors and windows.
