OL,3,CMan 'pointed out homes of migrant
OL,4,Cneighbours' for attacks, court told
OL,6,FA PSNI air support helicopter observed
OL,7,Fthe incident and directed officers on
OL,8,Fthe ground as they pursued suspects
OL,9,Ffrom the scene.
OL,11,FProsecution counsel alleged that the
OL,12,Ffootage showed Watson pointing out his
OL,13,Fneighbours believed to be foreign
OL,14,Fnationals.
OL,16,F"He was directing others towards the
OL,17,Fproperties and pointing out the homes
OL,18,Fof what were perceived to be
OL,19,Fmigrants," she contended.
