OL,3,CMan 'pointed out homes of migrant
OL,4,Cneighbours' for attacks, court told
OL,6,FWhen police detained Watson he had a
OL,7,Fbalaclava in his pocket, the court
OL,8,Fheard.
OL,10,FDuring interviews he claimed three
OL,11,Fmembers of the local UVF had
OL,12,Fapproached and asked him if he knew
OL,13,Fwhere anyone from outside the area
OL,14,Flived.
OL,16,FAccording to his account, he became
OL,17,Fscared, pointed towards his own house
OL,18,Fand asked the men not to break the
OL,19,Fwindows.
