OL,3,CMan 'pointed out homes of migrant
OL,4,Cneighbours' for attacks, court told
OL,6,FHe denied identifying the homes of any
OL,7,Fmigrants, insisting that he gets on
OL,8,Fwell with his neighbours.
OL,10,F"When asked why he had a balaclava he
OL,11,Fsaid he had been forced to take it by
OL,12,Fa local member of the UVF and that he
OL,13,Fwas terrified of the UVF," the
OL,14,Fprosecutor disclosed.
OL,16,F"But when he was asked why there was a
OL,17,FUVF flag outside his house he said
OL,18,Fthat was to commemorate the historical
OL,19,FUVF (founded in 1912) and had no
OL,20,Frelevance to the UVF he was apparently
OL,21,Fterrified of."
